snippet.title: Hampton Court (Official Trailer) - A Visual Novel Video Game Set in The Court of Henry VIII
snippet.description:
I've finished my visual novel game set in the court of Henry VIII. The year is 1539 and you are a princess from a abroad, sent to court to meet the king. Every choice you make in the game can influence your destiny. Be careful what you say! 

GET THE FULL GAME HERE (or try a demo): http://hamptoncourtgame.com

I hope you like the game!

Connect With Me:
https://chriscollinscreative.com

:)
